#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:9
msgid "Oracle Cloud上の開発用HTTPサーバにSSHトンネルでアクセスする方法"
msgstr ""
"How to access the development HTTP server on Oracle Cloud with an SSH tunnel"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:11
msgid ""
"Sphinx + ablog による静的サイトを Oracle Cloud 上の Ubuntu サーバで管理しているとき、 ``git push`` "
"前にローカルでの表示確認を行いたいケースがあります。 "
"外部からHTTPで直接アクセスできない状況でも、SSHトンネルを活用すれば開発中のサイトの確認が可能です。"
msgstr ""
"When managing a static site using Sphinx + ablog on an Ubuntu server on "
"Oracle Cloud, you may want to check the display locally before ``git push``."
" Even in situations where direct access via HTTP from the outside is not "
"possible, you can check the site under development by using an SSH tunnel."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:15
msgid ""
"この記事では、Oracle CloudのFree Tierインスタンスに立てたUbuntuサーバ上でHTTPサーバを一時的に起動し、 "
"SSHトンネルで自宅ブラウザから接続・確認する方法を紹介します。"
msgstr ""
"In this article, we will introduce how to temporarily start an HTTP server "
"on an Ubuntu server set up on an Oracle Cloud Free Tier instance, and "
"connect and check it from your home browser using an SSH tunnel."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:24
msgid "背景"
msgstr "background"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:26
msgid "サーバは Oracle Cloud の Always Free 枠で稼働"
msgstr "Servers run on Always Free tier in Oracle Cloud"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:27
msgid "Sphinx + ablog によるドキュメントやブログ記事をメンテナンス中"
msgstr "Maintaining documentation and blog articles using Sphinx + ablog"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:28
msgid "``make html`` 後の ``_build/html`` をブラウザで確認したい"
msgstr "I want to check ``_build/html`` after ``make html`` in a browser."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:29
msgid "ただし、開発用ポート（例: 8000）が外部に公開されておらず、直接アクセスできない"
msgstr ""
"However, the development port (e.g. 8000) is not exposed externally and "
"cannot be accessed directly."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:32
msgid "実現方法：SSHトンネル"
msgstr "How to achieve: SSH tunnel"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:34
msgid ""
"SSH接続が可能であれば、SSHの **ポートフォワーディング（ローカルフォワード）** 機能を使って、 サーバ内の "
"``localhost:8000`` を自宅の ``localhost:8000`` に見せることができます。"
msgstr ""
"If you have an SSH connection, you can use SSH's **port forwarding (local "
"forwarding)** feature to make ``localhost:8000`` on your server appear to be"
" ``localhost:8000`` at home."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:38
msgid "1. サーバ側で簡易HTTPサーバを起動"
msgstr "1. Start a simple HTTP server on the server side"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:45
msgid "サーバ内から ``curl http://localhost:8000`` で正常に応答することを確認します。"
msgstr ""
"Verify that ``curl http://localhost:8000`` responds correctly from within "
"the server."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:48
msgid "2. クライアント側（Windows）でSSHトンネルを張る"
msgstr "2. Create an SSH tunnel on the client side (Windows)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:50
msgid "PowerShell または コマンドプロンプトで以下を実行："
msgstr "Run the following in PowerShell or Command Prompt:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:56
msgid "``-i``：秘密鍵の指定"
msgstr "``-i``: Specify private key"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:57
msgid "``-L``：ローカルポート8000をサーバのlocalhost:8000に転送"
msgstr "``-L``: Forward local port 8000 to server localhost:8000"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:58
msgid "``-N``：コマンド実行せず、接続だけ行う"
msgstr "``-N``: Do not execute command, just connect"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:60
msgid ""
"成功すれば、**ブラウザで ``http://localhost:8000`` にアクセス** することで、 開発中のHTML出力を確認できます。"
msgstr ""
"If successful, you can check the HTML output during development by visiting "
"``http://localhost:8000`` in your browser."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:64
msgid "備考"
msgstr "remarks"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:66
msgid "SSHトンネルは接続中のみ有効。ターミナルを閉じると切断されます"
msgstr ""
"SSH tunnel is valid only while connected. Closing the terminal will "
"disconnect you"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:67
msgid "PuTTYでも同様の設定が可能（GUIでトンネルを追加）"
msgstr "Similar settings can be made with PuTTY (add tunnel via GUI)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:68
msgid "Oracle CloudのセキュリティリストやUFW設定を変更せずに利用可能"
msgstr ""
"Can be used without changing Oracle Cloud security list or UFW settings"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:71
msgid "まとめ"
msgstr "summary"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:73
msgid ""
"本手法により、Sphinx + ablog のサイトを **Gitにpushする前の状態で視覚的に確認できる方法** を整えることができました。"
msgstr ""
"Using this method, we were able to create a way to visually check the Sphinx"
" + ablog site before it was pushed to Git."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:82
msgid "外部公開せずに安全に開発環境を構築・確認する方法として、今後も活用できそうです。"
msgstr ""
"It looks like it will continue to be used in the future as a way to safely "
"build and check a development environment without disclosing it to the "
"outside world."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-12-ssh-tunnel-Http-Preview.rst:85
msgid ""
"Oracle Cloud 側でポート 8001 を外部公開する設定（セキュリティリストやUFWの調整）も試みましたが、 "
"接続確立できず、原因の特定に至りませんでした。ホスティングが目的ではないので諦めました。"
msgstr ""
"I tried setting up to expose port 8001 externally on the Oracle Cloud side "
"(adjusting the security list and UFW), but I was unable to establish a "
"connection and was unable to identify the cause. I gave up because hosting "
"was not my goal."

